PrecisAppointment of STEWART BECK as Consul General of Canada in Shanghai (People's Republic of China); RICHARD MANN as Ambassador of Canada to the State of Kuwait; PETER McKELLAR as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Latvia; JOHN MUNDY as Consul General of Canada at Sydney (Commonwealth of Australia); GUILLERMO RISHCHYNSKI as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; JOHN ROBINSON as High Commissioner for Canada to Jamaica with concurrent accreditation as Commissioner to the British Dependent Territories of the Cayman Islands and the Turks and Caicos Islands; and CHRISTOPHER WESTDAL as Alternate Permanent Representative and Ambassador of Canada to the Office of the United Nations, and Permanent Representative and Ambassador to the United Nations for Disarmament.
